<div class="inner" id="msg_630917">题记：<br><br>可能有很多朋友和我一样对FAQ不太敏感，事实上其中还是有很多对规则的关键解读的。<br>有兴趣的人可以看看 <a href="http://paizo.com/paizo/faq" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://paizo.com/paizo/faq</a><br><br><ul class="bbc_list" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg630918#msg630918" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">CRB（概论, GM规则, 种族与职业）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg630971#msg630971" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">CRB（专长与技能, 物品）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg632933#msg632933" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">CRB（法术与魔法）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg632936#msg632936" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">CRB（战斗）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg633097#msg633097" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">怪物图鉴（Bestiaries）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg632937#msg632937" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">进阶种族手册（Advanced Race Guide）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg632938#msg632938" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">进阶玩家手册（Advanced Player&#039;s Guide）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg632940#msg632940" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">进化职业手册（Advanced Class Guide）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg632941#msg632941" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">极限魔法（Ultimate Magic）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg632942#msg632942" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">极限战斗（Ultimate Combat）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg633094#msg633094" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">极限宝具（Ultimate Equipment） &amp; 极限战役（Ultimate Campaign）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg633095#msg633095" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">神话冒险（Mythic Adventures） &amp; 探索者解放（Pathfinder&nbsp; Unchained）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg745767#msg745767" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">异能冒险（Occult Adventures）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg827207#msg827207" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">极限诡道（Ultimate Intrigue）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg827210#msg827210" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">惧怖冒险（Horror Adventures）</a><li><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=67857.msg907790#msg907790" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">极限荒野（Ultimate Wilderness）<sup><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong>New！</strong></span></sup></a></ul><br>★ 查找最新更新时，请搜索【<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"><strong>New！</strong></span>】。</div>
