<a href="?PHPSESSID=19df664ebe9df249dcb3687c9a9fbfd6&amp;action=profile;u=40391" title="检视会员资料:  傻豆">傻豆</a>
</h4>
<ul class="reset smalltext" id="msg_745767_extra_info">
<li class="membergroup">版主<li class="stars"><img src="Themes/celeste/images/off.png" alt="*" border="0"/><li class="avatar" style="overflow: auto;">
